quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  5,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  5,1,ae imaan walo! apne iqraron ko poora karo. tumahray liye charpaye janwar ( jo charnay walay hain ) halal kar diye gay hain. bajuz un ke jo tumhe parh kar sunaye jatay hain magar ahram ( hajj ) mein shikaar ko halal nah janna. khuda jaissa chahta hai hukum deta hai
  5,2,momino! khuda ke naam ki cheezon ki be hurmati nah karna aur nah adab ke mahinay ki aur nah qurbani ke janwaron ki aur nah un janwaron ki ( jo khuda ki Nazar kar diye gay hon aur ) jin ke gulon mein pitay bandhay hon aur nah un logon ki jo izzat ke ghar ( yani beeet allah ) ko ja rahay hon ( aur ) apne perwar-digaar ke fazl aur is ki khushnodi ke tallab-gaar hon aur jab ahram utaar do to ( phir ikhtiyar hai ke ) shikaar karo aur logon ki dushmani is wajah se ke unhon ne tum ko izzat wali masjid se roka tha tumhe is baat par amaada nah kere ke tum un par zayad-ti karne lagu aur ( dekho ) neki aur parhaiz gari ke kamon mein aik dosray ki madadkiya karo aur gunah aur zulm ki baton mein madad nahkiya karo aur khuda se drtay raho. kuch shak nahi ke khuda ka azaab sakht hai
  5,3,tum par mra howa janwar aur ( behta ) lahoo aur soor ka gosht aur jis cheez par khuda ke siwa kisi aur ka naam puraka jaye aur jo janwar gala ghatt kar mar jaye aur jo chout lag kar mar jaye aur jo gir kar mar jaye aur jo seeng lag kar mar jaye yeh sab haraam hain aur woh janwar bhi jis ko diranday phaar khayen. magar jis ko tum ( marnay se pehlay ) zibah karlo aur woh janwar bhi jo thaan par zibahkiya jaye aur yeh bhi ke pason se qismat maloom karo yeh sab gunah ( ke kaam ) hain aaj kafir tumahray deen se na umeed ho gay hain to un se mat daro aur mujhi se drtay raho ( aur ) aaj hum ne tumahray liye tumhara deen kaamil kar diya aur apni naematain tum par poori kar den aur tumahray liye islam ko deen pasandkiya haan jo shakhs bhook mein nachar ho jaye ( bashart e kay ) gunah ki taraf mael nah ho to khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  5,4,tum se puchhte hain ke kon kon si cheezein un ke liye halal hain ( un se ) keh do ke sab pakeeza cheezein tum ko halal hain aur woh ( shikaar ) bhi halal hai jo tumahray liye un shikari janwaron ne pakra ho jin ko tum ne sdha rakha ho aur jis ( tareeq ) se khuda ne tumhe ( shikaar karna ) sikhaya hai ( is tareeq se ) tum ne un ko sikhaya ho to jo shikaar woh tumahray liye pakar rakhen is ko kha liya karo aur ( shikari janwaron ko chortay waqt ) khuda ka naam le liya karo aur khuda se drtay raho. be shak khuda jald hisaab lainay wala hai
  5,5,aaj tumahray liye sab pakeeza cheezein halal kar di gayeen aur ahal kitaab ka khana bhi tum ko halal hai aur tumhara khana un ko halal hai aur pak daman momin aurtain aur pak daman ahal kitaab aurtain bhi ( halal hain ) jabkay un ka mohar day do. aur un se Iffat qaim rakhni maqsood ho nah khuli badkaari karni aur nah chhupi dosti karni aur jo shakhs imaan se munhkir howa is ke amal zaya ho gay aur woh akhirat mein nuqsaan panay walon mein hoga
  5,5,kiya yeh zamana -e-jahliat ke hukum ke khwahish mand hain? aur jo yaqeen rakhtay hain un ke liye khuda se acha hukum kis ka hai ?
  5,5,ae imaan walo! yahood aur nasari ko dost nah banaao yeh aik dosray ke dost hain aur jo shakhs tum mein se un ko dost banaye ga woh bhi inhen mein se hoga bay shak khuda zalim logon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  5,5,to jin logon ke dilon mein ( nifaq ka ) marz hai tum un ko dekho ge ke un mein daud daud ke miley jatay hain kehte hain ke hamein khauf hai ke kahin hum par zamane ki gardish nah aajay so qareeb hai ke khuda fatah beje ya apne haan se koi aur amar ( nazil farmaiye ) phir yeh apne dil ki baton par jo chupaya karte they pasheman ho kar reh jayen ge
  5,5,aur is ( waqt ) musalman ( taajjub se ) kahin ge kekiya yeh wohi hain jo khuda ki sakht sakht kasmain khaya karte they ke hum tumahray sath hain un ke amal akart gay aur woh khasaray mein par gay
  5,5,ae imaan walo agar koi tum mein se apne deen se phir jaye ga to khuda aisay log peda kar day ga jin ko woh dost rakhay aur jisay woh dost rakhen aur jo mominon ke haq mein narmi karen aur kafiroon se sakhti se paish ayen khuda ki raah mein jehaad karen aur kisi malamat karne wali ki malamat se nah dareen yeh khuda ka fazl hai woh jisay chahta hai deta hai aur allah barri kashaish wala aur jan-nay wala hai
  5,5,tumahray dost to khuda aur is ke paighambar aur momin log hi hain jo namaz parhte aur zakaat dete aur ( khuda ke agay ) jhukatey hain
  5,5,aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke paighambar aur mominon se dosti kere ga to ( woh khuda ki jamaat mein daakhil hoga aur ) khuda ki jamaat hi ghalba panay wali hai
  5,5,ae imaan walon! jin logon ko tum se pehlay kitaaben di gayi theen un ko aur kafiroon ko jinhon ne tumahray deen ko hansi aur khail bana rakha hai dost nah banaao aur momin ho to khuda se drtay raho
  5,5,aur jab tum log namaz ke liye azaan dete ho to yeh usay bhi hansi aur khail banatay hain yeh is liye ke samajh nahi rakhtay
  5,5,kaho ke ae ahal kitaab! tum hum mein buraiee hikiya dekhte ho siwa is ke ke hum khuda par aur jo ( kitaab ) hum par nazil hui is par aur jo ( kitaaben ) pehlay nazil huien un par imaan laaye hain aur tum mein aksar badkirdar hain
  5,6,momino! jab tum namaz parhnay ka qasadkiya karo tum munh aur kohinyon taq haath dho liya karo aur sir ka maseh kar liya karo aur tikhno taq paon ( dho liya karo ) aur agar nahanay ki haajat ho to ( neha kar ) pak ho jaya karo aur agar bemaar ho ya safar mein ho ya koi tum mein se beeet al khala se ho kar aaya ho ya tum aurton se hum bistar hue ho aur tumhe pani nah mil sakay to pak matti lau aur is se munh aur hathon ka maseh ( yani tayamum ) kar lau. khuda tum par kisi terhan ki tangi nahi karna chahta balkay yeh chahta hai ke tumhe pak kere aur apni naematain tum par poori kere taakay tum shukar karo
  5,7,aur khuda ne jo tum par ahsaan kiye hain un ko yaad karo aur is ehad ko bhi jis ka tum se qoul liya tha ( yani ) jab tum ne kaha tha ke hum ne ( khuda ka hukum ) sun liya aur quboolkiya. aur allah se daro. kuch shak nahi ke khuda dilon ki baton ( taq ) se waaqif hai
  5,8,ae imaan walon! khuda ke liye insaaf ki gawahi dainay ke liye kharray ho jaya karo. aur logon ki dushmani tum ko is baat par amaada nah kere ke insaaf chore do. insaafkiya karo ke yahi parhaiz gari ki baat hai aur khuda se drtay raho. kuch shak nahi ke khuda tumahray sab aamaal se khabardaar hai
  5,9,jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay un se khuda ne wada farmaya hai ke un ke liye bakhshish aur ajar azeem hai
  5,10,aur jinhon ne kufarkiya aur hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya woh jahanumi hain
  5,11,ae imaan walo! khuda ne jo tum par ahsaankiya hai is ko yaad karo. jab aik jamaat ne iradahkiya ke tum par dast Darazi karen to is ne un ke haath rok diye aur khuda se drtay rahon aur momino ko khuda hi par bharosa rakhna chahiye
  5,12,aur khuda ne bani Israel se iqraar liya aur un mein hum ne baara sardar muqarrar kiye phir khuda ne farmaya ke mein tumahray sath hon agar tum namaz parhte aur zakaat dete raho ge aur mere payghambaroon par imaan lao ge aur un ki madad karo ge aur khuda ko qarz husna do ge to mein tum se tumahray gunah daur kar dun ga aur tum ko bahishtoon mein daakhil karoon ga jin ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hain phir jis ne is ke baad tum mein se kufarkiya woh seedhay raste se bhatak gaya
  5,13,to un logon ke ehad toar dainay ke sabab hum ne un par laanat ki aur un ke dilon ko sakht kar diya yeh log kalmaat ( kitaab ) ko apne maqamat se badal dete hain aur jin baton ki un ko nasiyaat ki gayi thi un ka bhi aik hissa faramosh kar baithy aur thoray admion ke siwa hamesha tum un ki ( aik nah aik ) khayanat ki khabar paate rehtay ho to un ki khataien maaf kardo aur ( un se ) dar guzar karo ke khuda ahsaan karne walon ko dost rakhta hai
  5,14,aur jo log ( apne tain ) kehte hain ke hum nasari hain hum ne un se bhi ehad liya tha magar unhon ne bhi is nasiyaat ka jo un ko ki gayi thi aik hissa faramosh kar diya to hum ne un ke baahum qayamat taq ke liye dushmani aur keena daal diya aur jo kuch woh karte rahay khuda anqareeb un ko is se aagah kere ga
  5,15,ae ahal kitaab! tumahray paas hamaray paighambar ( aakhir uz zamaan ) aa gay hain ke jo kuch tum kitaab ( Ellahi ) mein se chupatay they woh is mein se bohat kuch tumhe khol khol kar bta dete hain aur tumahray bohat se qasoor maaf kar dete hain be shak tumahray paas khuda ki taraf se noor aur roshan kitaab aa chuki hai
  5,16,jis se khuda apni Raza par chalne walon ko nijaat ke raste dekhata hai aur apne hukum se andheray mein se nikaal kar roshni ki taraf le jata aur un ko seedhay rasta par chalata hai
  5,17,jo log is baat ke qaail hain ke eesa ban maryam khuda hain woh be shak kafir hain ( un se ) keh do ke agar khuda eesa ban maryam ko aur un ki walida ko aur jitne log zameen mein hain sab ko halaak karna chahay to is ke agay kis ki paish chal sakti hai? aur aasman aur zameen aur jo kuch un dono mein hai sab par khuda hi ki badshahi hai woh jo chahta hai peda karta hai aur khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  5,18,aur yahood aur nasari kehte hain ke hum khuda ke betay aur is ke pyare hain kaho ke phir woh tumhari bdaamalyon ke sabab tumhen azaab kyun deta hai ( nahi ) balkay tum is ki makhloqaat mein ( dosaron ki terhan ke ) ensaan ho woh jisay chahay bakhshay aur jisay chahay azaab day aur aasman zameen aur jo kuch un dono mein hai sab par khuda hi ki hukoomat hai aur ( sab ko ) isi ki taraf lout kar jana hai
  5,19,ae ehley kitaab payghambaroon ke anay ka silsila jo ( aik arsay taq ) munhqita raha to ( ab ) tumahray paas hamaray paighambar aa gay hain jo tum se ( hamaray ehkaam ) bayan karte hain taakay tum yeh nah kaho ke hamaray paas koi khushkhabri ya dar sunanay wala nahi aaya so ( ab ) tumahray paas khushkhabri aur dar sunanay walay aa gay hain aur khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  5,20,aur jab moose ne apni qoum se kaha ke bhaio tum par khuda ne jo ahsaan kiye hain un ko yaad karo ke is ne tum mein paighambar peda kiye aur tumhe badshah banaya aur tum ko itna kuch inayatkiya ke ahal aalam mein se kisi ko nahi diya
  5,21,to bhaio! tum arz muqaddas ( yani malik shaam ) mein jisay khuda ne tumahray liye likh rakha hai chal daakhil ho aur ( dekhna muqablay ke waqt ) peeth nah phair dena warna nuqsaan mein par jao ge
  5,22,woh kehnay lagey ke moose! wahan to barray zabardast log ( rehtay ) hain aur jab taq woh is sarzamen se nikal nah jayen hum wahan ja nahi satke haan agar woh wahan se nikal jayen to hum ja daakhil hon ge
  5,23,jo log ( khuda se ) drtay they un mein se do shakhs jin par khuda ki inayat thi kehnay lagey ke un logon par darwazay ke raste se hamla kardo jab tum darwazay mein daakhil ho gay to fatah tumahray hai aur khuda hi par bharosa rakho bashart e kay sahib imaan ho
  5,24,woh bolay ke moose! jab taq woh log wahan hain hum kabhi wahan nahi ja satke ( agar larna hi zaroor hai ) to tum aur tumhara khuda jao aur laro hum yahin baithy rahen ge
  5,25,moose ne ( khuda se ) iltija ki ke perwar-digaar mein apne aur apne bhai ke siwa aur kisi par ikhtiyar nahi rakhta to hum mein aur un nafarman logon mein judai kardey
  5,26,khuda ne farmaya ke woh malik un par chalees baras taq ke liye haraam kar diya gaya ( ke wahan jaane nah payen ge aur jungle ki ) zameen mein srgrdan phirtay rahen ge to un nafarman logon ke haal par afsos nah karo
  5,27,aur ( ae Mohammad ) un ko aadam ke do beton ( Habil aur Qabeel ) ke halaat ( jo bilkul ) sachey ( hain ) parh kar suna do ke jab un dono ne khuda ( ki janab mein ) kuch niazain charhayen to aik ki niaz to qubool ho gayi aur dosray ki qubool nah hui ( tab Qabeel Habil se ) kehnay laga ke mein tujhe qatal karoon ga is ne kaha ke khuda parhaiz garon hi ki ( niaz ) qubool farmaya karta hai
  5,28,aur agar to mujhe qatal karne ke liye mujh par haath chalaye ga to mein tujh ko qatal karne ke liye tujh par haath nahi chlaon ga mujhe to khuday-e rab alameen se dar lagta hai
  5,29,mein chahta hon ke to mere gunah mein bhi makhoz ho aur apne gunah mein bhi phir ( Zumra ) ahal dozakh mein ho aur zaalmon ki yahi saza hai
  5,30,magar is ke nafs ne is ko bhai ke qatal hi ki targheeb di to is ne usay qatal kar diya aur khasara uthany walon mein ho gaya
  5,31,ab khuda ne aik kowa bheja jo zameen kurednay laga taakay usay dukhaay ke apne bhai ki laash ko kionkar chupaye kehnay laga ae hai mujh se itna bhi nah ho saka ke is kaway ke barabar hota ke apne bhai ki laash chhupa deta phir woh pasheman howa
  5,32,is qatal ki wajah se hum ne bani Israel par yeh hukum nazilkiya ke jo shakhs kisi ko ( na-haq ) qatal kere ga ( yani ) baghair is ke ke jaan ka badla liya jaye ya malik mein kharabi karne ki saza di jaye uss ne goya tamam logon ko qatalkiya aur jo is ki zindagani ka mojab howa to goya tamam logon ki zindagani ka mojab howa aur un logon ke paas hamaray paighambar roshan daleelen laa chuke hain phir is ke baad bhi un se bohat se log malik mein Had aitdaal se nikal jatay hain
  5,33,jo log khuda aur is ke rasool se larai karen aur malik mein fasaad karne ko dorrtay phrin un ki yahi saza hai ke qatal kar diye jayen ya suli charha diye jayen ya un ke aik aik taraf ke haath aur aik aik taraf ke paon kaat diye jayen ya malik se nikaal diye jayen yeh to duniya mein un ki ruswai hai aur akhirat mein un ke liye bara ( bhaari ) azaab tayyar hai
  5,34,haan jin logon ne is se peshtar ke tumahray qaboo mein aa jayen tauba kar li to jaan rakho ke khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  5,35,ae imaan walo! khuda se drtay raho aur is ka qurb haasil karne ka zareya talaash karte raho aur is ke raste mein jehaad karo taakay rstgari pao
  5,36,jo log kafir hain agar un ke paas roye zameen ( ke tamam khazanay aur is ) ka sab maal o mata'aho aur is ke sath isi qader aur bhi ho taakay qayamat ke roz azaab ( se rstgari haasil karne ) ka badla den to un se qubool nahikiya jaye ga aur un ko dard dainay wala azaab hoga
  5,37,( har chand ) chahain ge ke aag se nikal jayen magar is se nahi nikal saken ge aur un ke liye hamesha ka azaab hai
  5,38,aur jo chori kere mard ho ya aurat un ke haath kaat daalo yeh un ke failon (amloo) ki saza aur khuda ki taraf se Ibrat hai aur khuda zabardast ( aur ) sahib hikmat hai
  5,39,aur jo shakhs gunah ke baad tauba kere aur nekokaar ho jaye to khuda is ko maaf kar day ga kuch shak nahi ke khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  5,40,kiya tum ko maloom nahi ke asmano aur zameen mein khuda hi ki saltanat hai? jis ko chahay azaab kere aur jisay chahay bakhash day aur khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  5,41,ae paighambar! jo log kufar mein jaldi karte hain ( kuch to ) un mein se ( hain ) jo munh se kehte hain ke hum momin hain lekin un ke dil momin nahi hain aur ( kuch ) un mein se jo yahodi hain un ki wajah se ghumnaak nah hona yeh ghalat baatein bananay ke liye jasoosi karte phirtay hain aur aisay logon ( ke behkanay ) ke liye jasoos banay hain jo abhi tumahray paas nahi aeye ( sahih ) baton ko un ke maqamat ( mein saabit honay ) ke baad badal dete hain ( aur logon se ) kehte hain ke agar tum ko yahi ( hukum ) miley to usay qubool kar lena aur agar yeh nah miley to is se Ihtiraz karna aur agar kisi ko khuda gumraah karna chahay to is ke liye tum kuch bhi khuda se ( hadaayat ka ) ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay yeh woh log hain jin ke dilon ko khuda ne pak karna nahi chaha un ke liye duniya mein bhi zillat hai aur akhirat mein bhi bara azaab hai
  5,42,( yeh ) jhooti baatein bananay ke jasoosi karne walay aur ( rishwat ka ) haraam maal khanay walay hain agar yeh tumahray paas ( koi muqadma Faisal karanay ko ) ayen to tum un mein faisla kar dena ya aaraaz karna aur agar un se aaraaz karo ge to woh tumhara kuch bhi nahi bigaar saken ge aur agar faisla karna chaho to insaaf ka faisla karna ke khuda insaaf karne walon ko dost rakhta hai
  5,43,aur yeh tum se ( apne muqadmaat ) kionkar Faisal krayn ge jabkay khud un ke paas torat ( mojood ) hai jis mein khuda ka hukum ( likha howa ) hai ( yeh usay jantay hain ) phir is ke baad is se phir jatay hain aur yeh log imaan hi nahi rakhtay
  5,44,bay shak hum ne torait nazil farmai jis mein hadaayat aur roshni hai isi ke mutabiq anbia jo ( khuda ke ) farmanbardar they yahudion ko hukum dete rahay hain aur mashaiykh aur ulama bhi kyunkay woh kitaab khuda ke nigehbaan muqarrar kiye gay they aur is par gawah they ( yani hukum Ellahi ka yaqeen rakhtay they ) to tum logon se mat darna aur mujhi se drtay rehna aur meri ayaton ke badlay thori si qeemat nah lena aur jo khuda ke nazil farmaiye hue ehkaam ke mutabiq hukum nah day to aisay hi log kafir hain
  5,45,aur hum ne un logon ke liye torat mein yeh hukum likh diya tha ke jaan ke badlay jaan aur aankhh ke badlay aankhh aur naak ke badlay naak aur kaan ke badlay kaan aur daant ke badlay daant aur sab zakhamo ka isi terhan badla hai lekin jo shakhs badla maaf kar day woh is ke liye kaffara hoga aur jo khuda ke nazil farmaiye hue ehkaam ke mutabiq hukum nah day to aisay hi log be insaaf hain
  5,46,aur un payghambaroon ke baad unhi ke qadmon par hum ne eesa ban maryam ko bheja jo apne se pehlay ki kitaab torat ki tasdeeq karte they aur un ko injeel inayat ki jis mein hadaayat aur noor hai aur torat ki jo is se pehli kitaab ( hai ) tasdeeq karti hai aur parhaiz garon ko raah batati aur nasiyaat karti hai
  5,47,aur ahal injeel ko chahiye ke jo ehkaam khuda ne is mein nazil farmaiye hain is ke mutabiq hukum diya karen aur jo khuda ke nazil kiye hue ehkaam ke mutabiq hukum nah day ga to aisay log nafarman hain
  5,48,aur ( ae paighambar! ) hum ne tum par sachhi kitaab nazil ki hai jo apne se pehli kitabon ki tasdeeq karti hai aur un ( sab ) par shaamil hai to jo hukum khuda ne nazil farmaya hai is ke mutabiq un ka faisla karna aur haq jo tumahray paas aachuka hai is ko chore kar un ki khawahishon ki pairwi nah karna hum ne tum mein se har aik ( firqay ) ke liye aik dastoor aur tareeqa muqarrarkiya hai aur agar khuda chahta to sab ko aik hi Shariat par kar deta magar jo hukum is ne tum ko diye hain un mein woh tumhari azmaish karni chahta hai so naik kamon mein jaldi karo tum sab ko khuda ki taraf lout kar jana hai phir jin baton mein tum ko ikhtilaaf tha woh tum ko bta day ga
  5,49,aur ( hum phir takeed karte hain ke ) jo ( hukum ) khuda ne nazil farmaya hai isi ke mutabiq un mein faisla karna aur un ki khawahishon ki pairwi nah karna aur un se bachte rehna ke kisi hukum se jo khuda ne tum par nazil farmaya hai yeh kahin tum ko behka nah den agar yeh nah manen to jaan lau ke khuda chahta hai ke un ke baaz gunaaho ke sabab un par museebat nazil kere aur aksar log to nafarman hain
  5,60,kaho ke mein tumhe batau ke khuda ke haan is se bhi badter jaza panay walay kon hain? woh log hain jin par khuda ne laanat ki aur jin par woh ghazabnak howa aur ( jin ko ) un mein se bandar aur soor bana diya aur jinhon ne shetan ki parastish ki aisay logon ka bura thikana hai aur woh seedhay raste se bohat daur hain
  5,61,aur jab yeh log tumahray paas atay hain to kehte hain ke hum imaan le aeye halaank kufar le kar atay hain aur isi ko leker jatay hain aur jin baton ko yeh makhfi rakhtay hain khuda un ko khoob jaanta hai
  5,62,aur tum dekho ge ke un mein aksar gunah aur zayad-ti aur haraam khanay mein jaldi kar rahay hain be shak yeh jo kuch karte hain bura karte hain
  5,63,bhala un ke mashaiykh aur ulama inhen gunah ki baton aur haraam khanay se mana kyun nahi karte? bilashuba woh bhi bura karte hain
  5,64,aur yahood kehte hain ke khuda ka haath ( gardan se ) bandha howa hai ( yani allah bukheel hai ) inhen ke haath bandhay jayen aur aisa kehnay ke sabab un par laanat ho ( is ka haath bandha howa nahi ) balkay is ke dono haath khulay hain woh jis terhan ( aur jitna ) chahta hai kharch karta hai aur ( ae Mohammad ) yeh ( kitaab ) jo tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tum par nazil hui is se un mein se aksar ki shararat aur inkaar aur barhay ga aur hum ne un ke baahum adawat aur bughz qayamat taq ke liye daal diya hai yeh jab larai ke liye aag jalatay hain khuda is ko bujha deta hai aur yeh malik mein fasaad ke liye doray phirtay hain aur khuda fasaad karne walon ko dost nahi rakhta
  5,65,aur agar ahal kitaab imaan laatay aur parhaiz gari karte to hum un se un ke gunah mehv kar dete aur un ko Nemat ke baghoon mein daakhil karte
  5,66,aur agar woh torat aur injeel ko aur jo ( aur kitaaben ) un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se un par nazil huien un ko qaim rakhtay ( to un par rizaq meen ki terhan barasta ke ) apne oopar se paon ke neechay se khatay un mein kuch log miyana ro hain aur bohat se aisay hain jin ke aamaal buray hain
  5,67,ae paighambar jo arshadat khuda ki taraf se tum par nazil hue hain sab logon ko pouncha do aur agar aisa nahkiya to tum khuda ke pegham pohanchanay mein qaasir rahay ( yani paigambri ka farz ada nahkiya ) aur khuda tum ko logon se bachaaye rakhay ga bay shak khuda munkiron ko hadaayat nahi deta
  5,68,kaho ke ae ahal kitaab! jab taq tum torat aur injeel ko aur jo ( aur kitaaben ) tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tum logon par nazil huien un ko qaim nah rakho ge kuch bhi raah par nahi ho satke aur yeh ( quran ) jo tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tum par nazil howa hai un mein se aksar ki sar kashi aur kufar aur barhay ga to tum qoum kufar par afsos nah karo
  5,69,jo log khuda par aur roz akhirat par imaan layein ge aur amal naik karen ge khuwa woh musalman hon ya yahodi ya sitara parast ya isaai un ko ( qayamat ke din ) nah kuch khauf ho ga aur nah ghumnaak hon ge
  5,70,hum ne bani Israel se ehad bhi liya aur un ki taraf paighambar bhi beje ( lekin ) jab koi paighambar un ke paas aisi baatein le kar aata jin ko un ke dil nahi chahtay they to woh ( anbia ki ) aik jamaat ko to jhutla dete aur aik jamaat ko qatal kar dete they
  5,71,aur khayaal karte they ke ( is se un par ) koi aafat nahi anay ki to woh andhay aur behray ho gay phir khuda ne un par meharbani farmai ( lekin ) phir un mein se bohat se andhay aur behray ho gay aur khuda un ke sab kamon ko dekh raha hai
  5,72,woh log be shuba kafir hain jo kehte hain ke maryam ke betay ( eesa ) maseeh khuda hain halaank maseeh yahood se yeh kaha karte they ke ae bani Israel khuda hi ki ibadat karo jo mera bhi perwar-digaar hai aur tumhara bhi ( aur jaan rakho ke ) jo shakhs khuda ke sath shirk kere ga khuda is par bahisht haraam kar day ga aur is ka thikana dozakh hai aur zaalmon ka koi madadgaar nahi
  5,73,woh log ( bhi ) kafir hain jo is baat ke qaail hain ke khuda teen mein ka teesra hai halaank is mabood yaktaa ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi agar yeh log aisay aqwal ( o aqaid ) se baz nahi ayen ge to un mein jo kafir hue hain woh takleef dainay wala azaab payen ge
  5,74,to yeh kyun khuda ke agay tauba nahi karte aur is se gunaaho ki maffi nahi mangte aur khuda to bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  5,75,maseeh Ibn maryam to sirf ( khuda ) ke paighambar they un se pehlay bhi bohat se rasool guzar chuke they aur un ki walida ( maryam khuda ki ) walii aur sachhi farmanbardar theen dono ( ensaan they aur ) khana khatay they dekho hum un logon ke liye apni ayatain kis terhan khol khol kar bayan karte hain phir ( yeh ) dekho ke yeh kidhar ultay ja rahay hain
  5,76,kaho ke tum khuda ke siwa aisi cheez ki kyun parastish karte ho jis ko tumahray naffa aur nuqsaan ka kuch bhi ikhtiyar nahi? aur khuda hi ( sab kuch ) santa jaanta hai
  5,77,kaho ke ae ahal kitaab! apne deen ( ki baat ) mein na-haq mubaligha nah karo aur aisay logon ki khawahishon ke peechay nah chalo jo ( khud bhi ) pehlay gumraah hue aur aur bhi aksaron ko gumraah kar gay aur seedhay raste se bhatak gay
  5,78,jo log bani Israel mein kafir hue un par dawod aur eesa ban maryam ki zabaan se laanat ki gayi yeh is liye ke nafarmani karte they aur hadd se tajawaz karte they
  5,79,( aur ) buray kamon se jo woh karte they aik dosray ko roktay nahi they bilashuba woh bura karte they
  5,80,tum un mein se bahuton ko dekho ge ke kafiroon se dosti rakhtay hain unhon ne jo kuch apne wastay agay bheja hai bura hai ( woh yeh ) ke khuda un se nakhush howa aur woh hamesha azaab mein ( mubtala ) rahen ge
  5,81,aur agar woh khuda par aur paighambar par aur jo kitaab un par nazil hui thi is par yaqeen rakhtay to un logon ko dost nah banatay lekin un mein aksar badkirdar hain
  5,82,( ae peghambar sallallahu alaihi wasallam ) tum dekho ge ke mominon ke sath sab se ziyada dushmani karne walay yahodi aur mushriq hain aur dosti ke lehaaz se mominon se qareeb tar un logon ko pao ge jo kehte hain ke hum nasari hain yeh is liye ke un mein aalam bhi hain aur mashaiykh bhi aur woh taqqabur nahi karte
  5,83,aur jab is ( kitaab ) ko suntay hain jo ( sab se pehlay ) paighambar ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) par nazil hui to tum dekhte ho ke un ki aankhon se ansoo jari ho jatay hain is liye ke unhon ne haq baat pehchan li aur woh ( khuda ki janab mein ) arz karte hain ke ae perwar-digaar hum imaan le aeye to hum ko maan-ne walon mein likh le
  5,84,aur hameinkiya howa hai ke khuda par aur haq baat par jo hamaray paas aayi hai imaan nah layein aur hum umeed rakhtay hain ke perwar-digaar hum ko naik bundon ke sath ( bahisht mein ) daakhil kere ga
  5,85,to khuda ne un ko is kehnay ke aiwz ( bahisht ke ) baagh ataa farmaiye jin ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hain woh hamesha un mein rahen ge aur naiko karon ka yahi sila hai
  5,86,aur jin logon ne kufarkiya aur hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya woh jahanumi hain
  5,87,momino! jo pakeeza cheezein khuda ne tumahray liye halal ki hain un ko haraam nah karo aur hadd se nah badho ke khuda hadd se bherne walon ko dost nahi rakhta
  5,88,aur jo halal tayyab rozi khuda ne tum ko di hai usay khao aur khuda se jis par imaan rakhtay ho drtay raho
  5,89,khuda tumhari be iradah qasmon par tum se muwakhza nahi kere ga lekin pukhta qasmon par ( jin ke khilaaf karo ge ) muwakhza kere ga to is ka kaffara das mohtajon ko ost darjay ka khana khilana hai jo tum apne ahal vayal ko khelati ho ya un ko kapray dena ya aik ghulam azad karna aur jis ko muyassar nah ho woh teen rozay rakhay yeh tumhari qasmon ka kaffara hai jab tum qasam kha lo ( aur usay toar do ) aur ( tum ko ) chahiye ke apni qasmon ki hifazat karo is terhan khuda tumahray ( samjhane ke ) liye apni ayatain khol khol kar bayan farmata hai taakay tum shukar karo
  5,90,ae imaan walo! sharaab aur juaa aur buut aur paasay ( yeh sab ) napak kaam aamaal shetan se hain so un se bachte rehna taakay nijaat pao
  5,91,shetan to yeh chahta hai ke sharaab aur juye ke sabab tumahray aapas mein dushmani aur ranjish dalwa day aur tumhe khuda ki yaad se aur namaz se rok day to tum ko ( un kamon se ) baz rehna chahiye
  5,92,aur khuda ki farmabardari aur rsolِ ( khuda ) ki itaat karte raho aur drtay raho agar munh phero ge to jaan rakho ke hamaray paighambar ke zimmay to sirf pegham ka khol kar pouncha dena hai
  5,93,jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay un par un cheezon ka kuch gunah nahi jo woh kha chuke jab ke unhon ne parhaizkiya aur imaan laaye aur naik kaam kiye phir parhaizkiya aur imaan laaye phir parhaizkiya aur naiko kaari ki aur khuda naiko karon ko dost rakhta hai
  5,94,momino! kisi qader shikaar se jin ko tum hathon aur naizon se pakar sakuu khuda tumhari azmaish kere ga ( yani haalat ahram mein shikaar ki momanat se ) taa ke maloom kere ke is se ghayebana kon darta hai to jo is ke baad zayad-ti kere is ke liye dukh dainay wala azaab ( tayyar ) hai
  5,95,momino! jab tum ahram ki haalat mein ho to shikaar nah maarna aur jo tum mein se jaan boojh kar usay maaray to ( ya to is ka ) badla ( day aur woh yeh hai ke ) isi terhan ka چارپایہ jisay tum mein do mooatbar shakhs muqarrar kar dein qurbani ( kere aur yeh qurbani ) kaabay pohanchai jaye ya kaffara ( day aur woh ) miskeeno ko khana khilana ( hai ) ya is ke barabar rozay rakhay taakay apne kaam ki saza ( ka maza ) chakhay ( aur ) jo pehlay ho chuka woh khuda ne maaf kar diya aur jo phir ( aisa kaam ) kere ga to khuda is se intiqam le ga aur khuda ghalib aur intiqam lainay wala hai
  5,96,tumahray liye darya ( ki cheezon ) ka shikaar aur un ka khana halal kar diya gaya hai ( yani ) tumahray aur musafiron ke faiday ke liye aur jungle ( ki cheezon ) ka shikaar jab taq tum ahram ki haalat mein raho tum par haraam hai aur khuda se jis ke paas tum ( sab ) jama kiye jao ge drtay raho
  5,97,khuda ne izzat ke ghar ( yani ) kaabay ko logon ke liye mojab aman muqarrar farmaya hai aur izzat ke mahino ko aur qurbani ko aur un janwaron ko jin ke gilaay mein pitay bandhay hon yeh is liye ke tum jaan lau ke jo kuch asmano mein aur jo kuch zameen mein hai khuda sab ko jaanta hai aur yeh ke khuda ko har cheez ka ilm hai
  5,98,jaan rakho ke khuda sakht azab dainay wala hai aur yeh ke khuda bakhsnay wala meharban bhi hai
  5,99,paighambar ke zimmay to sirf pegham khuda ka pouncha dena hai aur jo kuch tum zahir karte ho aur jo kuch makhfi karte ho khuda ko sab maloom hai
  5,100,keh do ke napak cheezein aur pak cheezein barabar nahi hoten go napak cheezon ki kasrat tumhe khush hi lagey to aqal walo khuda se drtay raho taakay rstgari haasil karo
  5,101,momino! aisi cheezon ke baray mein mat sawal karo ke agar ( un ki haqeqteen ) tum par zahir kar di jayen to tumhe buri lagen aur agar quran ke nazil honay ke ayyaam mein aisi baatein pucho ge to tum par zahir bhi kar di jayen gi ( ab to ) khuda ne aisi baton ( ke poochnay ) se dar guzar farmaya hai aur khuda bakhsnay wala Burdbar hai
  5,102,is terhan ki baatein tum se pehlay logon ne bhi poochi theen ( magar jab batayi gayeen to ) phir un se munhkir ho gay
  5,103,khuda ne nah to bahera kuch cheez banaya hai aur nah saiba aur nah vaseela aur nah Haam balkay kafir khuda par jhoot aftara karte hain aur yeh aksar aqal nahi rakhtay
  5,104,aur jab un logon se kaha jata hai ke jo ( kitaab ) khuda ne nazil farmai hai is ki aur rasool allah ki taraf rujoo karo to kehte hain ke jis tareeq par hum ne apne baap dada ko paaya hai wohi hamein kaafi hai bhala agar un ke baap dada nah to kuch jantay hon aur nah seedhay raste par hon ( tab bhi? )
  5,105,ae imaan walo! apni jaanun ki hifazat karo jab tum hadaayat par ho to koi gumraah tumhara kuch bhi bigaar nahi sakta tum sab ko khuda ki taraf lout kar jana hai is waqt woh tum ko tumahray sab kamon se jo ( duniya mein ) kiye they aagah kere ga ( aur un ka badla day ga )
  5,106,momino! jab tum mein se kisi ki mout aa maujood ho to shahadat ( ka nisaab ) yeh hai ke wasiyat ke waqt tum ( musalmanoon ) mein se do adil ( yani sahib aitbaar ) gawah hon ya agar ( musalman nah milein aur ) tum safar kar rahay ho aur ( is waqt ) tum par mout ki museebat waqay ho to kisi dosray mazhab ke do ( shakhson ko ) gawah ( kar lau ) agar tum ko un gawahoon ki nisbat kuch shak ho to un ko ( asar ki ) namaz ke baad khara karo aur dono khuda ki kasmain khayen ke hum shahadat ka kuch aiwz nahi len ge go hamara rishta daar hi ho aur nah hum allah ki shahadat ko chupayen ge agar aisa karen ge to gunehgaar hon ge
  5,107,phir agar maloom ho jaye ke un dono ne ( jhoot bol kar ) gunah haasilkiya hai to jin logon ka unhon ne haq maarna chaha tha un mein se un ki jagah aur do gawah kharray hon jo ( maiyat se ) qaraabat قریبہ rakhtay hon phir woh khuda ki kasmain khayen ke hamari shahadat un ki shahadat se bohat achi hai aur hum ne koi zayad-ti nahi ki aisakiya ho to hum be insaaf hain
  5,108,is tareeq se bohat qareeb hai ke yeh log sahih sahih shahadat den ya is baat se khauf karen ke ( hamari ) kasmain un ki qasmon ke baad radd kar di jayen gi aur khuda se daro aur is ke hukmon ko ( gosh hosh se ) suno aur khuda nafarman logon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  5,109,( woh din yaad rakhnay ke Laiq hai ) jis din khuda payghambaroon ko jama kere ga phir un se pouchye ga ke tumhekiya jawab mila tha woh arz karen ge ke hamein kuch maloom nahi tuhi ghaib ki baton se waaqif hai
  5,110,jab khuda ( eesa se ) farmaiye ga ke ae eesa ban maryam! mere un ehsaanon ko yaad karo jo mein ne tum par aur tumhari walida par kiye jab mein ne rooh al quds ( yani jibrael ) se tumhari madad ki tum jhulay mein aur jawan ho kar ( aik hi nasq par ) logon se guftagu karte they aur jab mein ne tum ko kitaab aur danai aur torat aur injeel sikhayi aur jab tum mere hukum se matti ka janwar bana kar is mein phoonk maar dete they to woh mere hukum se urrnay lagta tha aur madar zaad andhay aur safaid daagh walay ko mere hukum se changa kar dete they aur murdy ko mere hukum se ( zindah karkay qabar se ) nikaal khara karte they aur jab mein ne bani Israel ( ke hathon ) ko tum se rok diya jab tum un ke paas khulay nishaan le kar aeye to jo un mein se kafir they kehnay lagey ke yeh Sarih jaadoo hai
  5,111,aur jab mein ne hawarion ki taraf hukum bheja ke mujh par aur mere paighambar par imaan lao woh kehnay lagey ke ( perwar-digaar ) hum imaan laaye to Shahid rahev ke hum farmanbardar hain
  5,112,( woh qissa bhi yaad karo ) jab hawarion ne kaha ke ae eesa ban maryam!kiya tumhara perwar-digaar aisa kar sakta hai ke hum par aasman se ( ta-aam ka ) khawan nazil kere? unhon ne kaha ke agar imaan rakhtay ho to khuda se daro
  5,113,woh bolay ke hamari yeh khwahish hai ke hum is mein se khayen aur hamaray dil tasalii payen aur hum jaan len ke tum ne hum se sach kaha hai aur hum is ( khawan ke nuzool ) par gawah rahen
  5,114,( tab ) eesa ban maryam ne dua ki ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar! hum par aasman se khawan nazil farma ke hamaray liye ( woh din ) eid qarar paye yani hamaray uglo aur pichlon ( sab ) ke liye aur woh teri taraf se nishani ho aur hamein rizaq day to behtar rizaq dainay wala hai
  5,115,khuda ne farmaya mein tum par zaroor khawan nazil frmaon ga lekin jo is ke baad tum mein se kufar kere ga usay aisa azaab dun ga ke ahal aalam mein kisi ko aisa azaab nah dun ga
  5,116,aur ( is waqt ko bhi yaad rakho ) jab khuda farmaiye ga ke ae eesa ban maryam!kiya tum ne logon se kaha tha ke khuda ke siwa mujhe aur meri walida ko mabood muqarrar karo? woh kahin ge ke to pak hai mujhe kab Shayaan tha ke mein aisi baat kehta jis ka mujhe kuch haq nahi agar mein ne aisa kaha hoga to tujh ko maloom hoga ( kyunkay ) jo baat mere dil mein hai to usay jaanta hai aur jo tairay zameer mein hai usay mein nahi jaanta be shak to allam الغیوب hai
  5,117,mein ne un se kuch nahi kaha bajuz is ke jis ka to ne mujhe hukum diya hai woh yeh ke tum khuda ki ibadat karo jo mera aur tumhara sab ka perwar-digaar hai aur jab taq mein un mein raha un ( ke halaat ) ki khabar rakhta raha jab to ne mujhe duniya se utha liya to to un ka nigran tha aur to har cheez se khabardaar hai
  5,118,agar to un ko azaab day to yeh tairay bande hain aur agar bakhash day to ( teri meharbani hai ) be shak to ghalib aur hikmat wala hai
  5,119,khuda farmaiye ga ke aaj woh din hai ke raast bazoo ko un ki sachaai hi faida day gi un ke liye baagh hain jin ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hain abdul aabad (hameha) un mein baste rahen ge khuda un se khush hai aur woh khuda se khush hain yeh barri kamyabi hai
  5,120,aasman aur zameen aur jo kuch un ( dono ) mein hai sab par khuda hi ki badshahi hai aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai
